Charlotte Kate Fox https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charlotte_Kate_Fox 0 Charlotte Kate Fox (born August 14, 1985) is an American film, TV, and theatrical actress and musician. She was cast as the first non-Japanese heroine of an NHK Asadora: the series Massan broadcast on Japanese television.
